Name: mem_offs
Description: Memory offset without a modrm byte (eg. #(c:MOV AL,[offset])#)

Name: mem_mpx
Description: Memory (modrm), MPX:#(p:)#16/32-bit mode: must be 32-bit addressing#(p:)#64-bit mode: 64-bit addressing is forced

Name: mem_mib
Description: Memory (modrm), MPX:#(p:)#16/32-bit mode: must be 32-bit addressing#(p:)#64-bit mode: 64-bit addressing is forced and must not be RIP relative

Name: r32_or_mem_mpx
Description: 32-bit GPR or memory, MPX: 16/32-bit mode: must be 32-bit addressing, 64-bit mode: 64-bit addressing is forced

Name: r64_or_mem_mpx
Description: 64-bit GPR or memory, MPX: 16/32-bit mode: must be 32-bit addressing, 64-bit mode: 64-bit addressing is forced

Name: bnd_or_mem_mpx
Description: BND register or memory, MPX: 16/32-bit mode: must be 32-bit addressing, 64-bit mode: 64-bit addressing is forced

Name: r8_reg
Description: 8-bit GPR encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte

Name: r8_opcode
Description: 8-bit GPR encoded in the low 3 bits of the opcode

Name: r16_reg
Description: 16-bit GPR encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte

Name: r16_reg_mem
Description: 16-bit GPR encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte. This is a memory operand and it uses the address size prefix (#(c:67h)#) not the operand size prefix (#(c:66h)#).

Name: r16_rm
Description: 16-bit GPR encoded in the #(c:mod + r/m)# fields of the modrm byte

Name: r16_opcode
Description: 16-bit GPR encoded in the low 3 bits of the opcode

Name: r32_reg
Description: 32-bit GPR encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte

Name: r32_reg_mem
Description: 32-bit GPR encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte. This is a memory operand and it uses the address size prefix (#(c:67h)#) not the operand size prefix (#(c:66h)#).

Name: r32_rm
Description: 32-bit GPR encoded in the #(c:mod + r/m)# fields of the modrm byte

Name: r32_opcode
Description: 32-bit GPR encoded in the low 3 bits of the opcode

Name: r32_vvvv
Description: 32-bit GPR encoded in the the #(c:V'vvvv)# field (VEX/EVEX/XOP)

Name: r64_reg
Description: 64-bit GPR encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte

Name: r64_reg_mem
Description: 64-bit GPR encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte. This is a memory operand and it uses the address size prefix (#(c:67h)#) not the operand size prefix (#(c:66h)#).

Name: r64_rm
Description: 64-bit GPR encoded in the #(c:mod + r/m)# fields of the modrm byte

Name: r64_opcode
Description: 64-bit GPR encoded in the low 3 bits of the opcode

Name: r64_vvvv
Description: 64-bit GPR encoded in the the #(c:V'vvvv)# field (VEX/EVEX/XOP)

Name: seg_reg
Description: Segment register encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte

Name: k_reg
Description: K register encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte

Name: kp1_reg
Description: K register (+1) encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte

Name: k_rm
Description: K register encoded in the #(c:mod + r/m)# fields of the modrm byte

Name: k_vvvv
Description: K register encoded in the the #(c:V'vvvv)# field (VEX/EVEX/XOP)

Name: mm_reg
Description: MM register encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte

Name: mm_rm
Description: MM register encoded in the #(c:mod + r/m)# fields of the modrm byte

Name: xmm_reg
Description: XMM register encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte

Name: xmm_rm
Description: XMM register encoded in the #(c:mod + r/m)# fields of the modrm byte

Name: xmm_vvvv
Description: XMM register encoded in the the #(c:V'vvvv)# field (VEX/EVEX/XOP)

Name: xmmp3_vvvv
Description: XMM register (+3) encoded in the the #(c:V'vvvv)# field (VEX/EVEX/XOP)

Name: xmm_is4
Description: XMM register encoded in the the high 4 bits of the last 8-bit immediate (VEX/XOP only so only XMM0-XMM15)

Name: xmm_is5
Description: XMM register encoded in the the high 4 bits of the last 8-bit immediate (VEX/XOP only so only XMM0-XMM15)

Name: ymm_reg
Description: YMM register encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte

Name: ymm_rm
Description: YMM register encoded in the #(c:mod + r/m)# fields of the modrm byte

Name: ymm_vvvv
Description: YMM register encoded in the the #(c:V'vvvv)# field (VEX/EVEX/XOP)

Name: ymm_is4
Description: YMM register encoded in the the high 4 bits of the last 8-bit immediate (VEX/XOP only so only YMM0-YMM15)

Name: ymm_is5
Description: YMM register encoded in the the high 4 bits of the last 8-bit immediate (VEX/XOP only so only YMM0-YMM15)

Name: zmm_reg
Description: ZMM register encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte

Name: zmm_rm
Description: ZMM register encoded in the #(c:mod + r/m)# fields of the modrm byte

Name: zmm_vvvv
Description: ZMM register encoded in the the #(c:V'vvvv)# field (VEX/EVEX/XOP)

Name: zmmp3_vvvv
Description: ZMM register (+3) encoded in the the #(c:V'vvvv)# field (VEX/EVEX/XOP)

Name: cr_reg
Description: CR register encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte

Name: dr_reg
Description: DR register encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte

Name: tr_reg
Description: TR register encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte

Name: bnd_reg
Description: BND register encoded in the #(c:reg)# field of the modrm byte

Name: sti_opcode
Description: ST(i) register encoded in the low 3 bits of the opcode

Name: imm2_m2z
Description: 2-bit immediate (m2z field, low 2 bits of the /is5 immediate, eg. #(c:VPERMIL2PS)#)
